channel.title: Sushi Dish
channel.description: Probably one of my last metaseq models, I dl'd C4D today and plan on using it. I went to a random object generator, and it told me "Spicy tuna roll". So I took that to the best of my abilities, and here you have it. Enjoy your sushi! [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/24pihys.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/1zej9mb.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/35lyr0o.jpg[/img]
